/procedure-definitions.html#Procedure.used&quot; title=&quot;Procedure.used : Identifies medications, devices and any other substance used as part of the procedure.&quot; data-no-external=&quot;true&quot;&gt;used&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;XProcedure.used&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: #F7F7F7&quot; id=&quot;a26.&quot; data-fhir=&quot;generated-heirarchy&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-space: nowrap; background-image: url(tbl_bck00.png)&quot; class=&quot;hierarchy&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://build.fhir.org/tbl_spacer.png&quot; alt=&quot;.&quot; style=&quot;background-color: inherit&quot; class=&quot;hierarchy&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://build.fhir.org/tbl_vjoin_end.png&quot; alt=&quot;.&quot; style=&quot;background-color: inherit&quot; class=&quot;hierarchy&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://build.fhir.org/icon_reference.png&quot; alt=&quot;.&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #F7F7F7; background-color: inherit&quot; title=&quot;Reference to another Resource&quot; class=&quot;hierarchy&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.fhir.org/procedure-definitions.html#Procedure.supportingInfo&quot; title=&quot;Procedure.supportingInfo : Other resources from the patient record that may be relevant to the procedure.  The information from these resources was either used to create the instance or is provided to help with its interpretation. This extension should not be used if more specific inline elements or extensions are available.&quot; data-no-external=&quot;true&quot;&gt;supportingInfo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;XProcedure.supportingInfo&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;" link="&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;border: 0p